column12:
'desc': [u'

Tollyjoy Baby Liners (100 Pieces) Price: Rs.309

Parents will always try to get the best possible for their little angels. Nappies and diapers can cause rashes on an infant’s delicate skin owing to excessive moisture trapped in it. The Tollyjoy Baby Liners are made to lessen the consequences created by diapers on a baby’s skin. These Tollyjoy Liners will help in keeping your bundle of joy’s tush dry and free of irritations. Made of soft material these Baby Liners are gentle on an infant’s delicate skin and will aid in keeping the skin supple and soft. These Liners from Tollyjoy will easily fit on to any nappy and minimize the back-flow of urine. The Tollyjoy Liners will also absorb a considerable amount of the baby’s poop and thus prevent the nappy from griming.

With these Baby Liners from Tollyjoy you can now feel tension free and be assured that your tiny tot is comfortable and absolutely free of nappy rashes. These disposable Baby Liners are very convenient to use as they have a snug fit to the baby’s body and are compatible with all kinds of baby wears. Make sure you keep your little angel dry and comfortable with the Tollyjoy Baby Liner.

']

Tollyjoy Unscented Wet Wipes (70 Pieces) Price: Rs.579

Baby wipes can be used on a child’s delicate skin to clean them after nappy changes. Using a wet wipe is better than washing as it will not rip the essential oils form the skin like frequent washing does. The Unscented Baby Wipes from Tollyjoy are enhanced with mild ingredients to prevent your tiny tot’s skin from drying out. The extracts of Aloe vera in these Wet Wipes make them good skin moisturizers that will keep your bundle of joy’s skin adequately hydrated. This component in the Tollyjoy Unscented Baby Wipe will help soothe and cool down your infant’s skin.\xa0These ISO certified and approved by the European Pharmacopoeia wet tissues have a pH balance of 5.5 that suits the skin perfectly.

Tollyjoy Pure Wipes (70 Pieces) Price: Rs.609

Wet wipes are widely used to cleanse an infant’s skin after nappy changes. This alternative to washing the baby’s skin prevents the loss of essential oils from the skin. The pure wipes from Tollyjoy are formulated with a very mild formula that will be gentle on your bundle of joy’s skin. These Pure Wipes from Tollyjoy are enriched with extracts of Aloe vera that is a well-known natural moisturizer. This will help in keeping your little one’s skin moisturized and nourished. It will also provide a cooling and soothing effect to the infant’s delicate skin.

The Tollyjoy Pure Wipes are absolutely alcohol free which makes them perfectly fit for use for your little angels. The hypoallergenic ingredients and pharmaceutical grade non-woven materials used in the making of these Pure Wipes ensure their safeness on your tiny tot’s skin. This can be used by all members of the family to cleanse the skin and hands of dirt. The convenient pack in which these unscented Tollyjoy Wet Wipes are packaged makes their portability and use extremely easy. The resealable pack will seal in the moisture of the wipes and keep them from drying out.
